Pathway explored : REACTOME EXPORT OF VIRAL RIBONUCLEOPROTEINS FROM NUCLEUS

This pathway contain 32 genes.

In these 32 genes for each day and cell type, they are not all expressed and they are not all differentially expressed between old versus young.
